	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you’re a mother, the Father’s Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> You wake before everyone, carry the invisible to-do list no one else can see, and give until there’s nothing left — often while quietly wondering if you’re doing enough. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father’s Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on any phone — and it reveals God not only as Father, but as the One who says, “as a mother comforts her child, so I will comfort you.” Whether you’re searching for “Bible verses for mothers,” encouragement for mom guilt, or rest for a depleted heart, it begins in one place: before you are anyone’s mother, you are your Father’s beloved daughter.`}
	keyTakeaway={`You cannot give a mothering you have not received. Before you are anyone’s mother, you are God’s beloved daughter — so come and be mothered by your Father first, and mother your family from the overflow.`}
	painsHeading={`The weight mothers carry`}
	painsIntroHtml={`Behind the snacks packed and the appointments remembered and the endless quiet management of a whole household, many mothers are running on empty. The mental load is invisible, the guilt is constant, and the comparison is relentless — and the one who comforts everyone else often has no one comforting her.`}
	painStats={[
