	whyHeading={`Why the Father's Heart Bible™ for mothers`}
	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet a God who is both Father and comforter`, bodyHtml: `Every other Bible names Him “God.” The Father’s Heart Bible™ reveals Him as <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — and lets you hear the One who comforts <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/66" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">“as a mother comforts her child.”</a> When the God you trust your children to has a Father’s heart, your reading becomes intimacy before it becomes instruction.` },
		{ heading: `It refills the one who pours out`, bodyHtml: `Free to <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">read online</a> with audio on every chapter, it’s built for a mother’s real day — listen while you nurse, fold, or drive, and let Scripture mother <em>you</em> in the in-between moments, before you give anything to anyone else.` },
